---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Farhan Hussain | Developer Relations & Technical Content Creator"
	description="Farhan Hussain is a Developer Relations professional and Technical Content Creator specializing in AI agents, machine learning, local LLMs, tutorials, and technical education."
>
	<section class="mb-20 grid min-w-0 items-center gap-10 border-b border-slate-200/80 pb-14 md:mb-24 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:gap-14 md:pb-16">
		<div class="min-w-0 max-w-3xl text-center md:text-left">
			<p class="mb-4 inline-flex max-w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1 text-[0.68rem] font-semibold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wider text-emerald-700 sm:text-xs">
				Developer Relations + Technical Content
			</p>
			<h1 class="mb-6 break-words text-[2.35rem] font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
				Hi, I'm <span class="text-indigo-600">Farhan Hussain</span>.
			</h1>
			<p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 md:mx-0 md:text-xl">
				I'm a Developer Relations professional and Technical Content Creator. 
				I specialize in bridging the gap between developers and products through 
				clear, engaging, and highly technical content, tutorials, and talks.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col items-stretch justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row md:justify-start">
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/farhan-hussain/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-600 focus:ring-offset-2">
					Let's connect
				</a>
				<a href="#featured-content" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-300 focus:ring-offset-2">
					View featured work
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mx-auto md:mx-0">
			<img 
				src="/farhanprofile.jpg" 
				alt="Farhan Hussain Profile" 
				class="h-36 w-36 rounded-full border-4 border-white object-cover shadow-xl ring-1 ring-slate-200 sm:h-44 sm:w-44 md:h-52 md:w-52"
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Featured Content Section -->
	<section id="featured-content" class="mb-20 scroll-mt-8 md:mb-24">
		<div class="mb-8 flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-end">
			<div>
				<p class="mb-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-indigo-600">Selected work</p>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-3xl">
					Featured Content
				</h2>
			</div>
			<p class="max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
				Tutorials and articles across AI agents, local LLMs, and practical developer workflows.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<!-- Video Card 1 -->
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OEnY7S8YPY" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-red-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-red-100 bg-red-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-red-600">Video</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Copilot Studio</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">Build Your First AI Agent That Can Send Emails</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">In this video we will explore how Microsoft Copilot Studio allows you to build an AI agent that can send emails on your behalf from scratch.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Watch Video <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Video Card 2 -->
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LJMqT-FZOXs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-red-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-red-100 bg-red-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-red-600">Video</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Ollama</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">How to Run DeepSeek R1 Locally</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">Discover how to run DeepSeek R1 locally on your own hardware using Ollama.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Watch Video <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Article Card 1 -->
			<a href="https://www.schoolofmachinelearning.com/2023/10/03/how-to-run-llms-locally-on-your-laptop-using-ollama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600">Article</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Machine Learning</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">How To Run LLMs Locally On Your Laptop</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">A step-by-step guide on how to run large language models (LLMs) on a laptop or desktop locally without powerful GPUs using Ollama.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Read Article <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Article Card 2 -->
			<a href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azurecommunicationservicesblog/build-your-ai-email-agent-with-microsoft-copilot-studio/4448724" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600">Article</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">MS Tech Community</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">Build Your AI Email Agent with Copilot Studio</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">A comprehensive tutorial on how to create an AI agent that can send emails on your behalf using Microsoft Copilot Studio and robust backend tools.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Read Article <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Article Card 3 -->
			<a href="https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azurecommunicationservicesblog/build-an-ai-email-responder-with-openai-and-azure-communication-services/4421127" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600">Article</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">MS Tech Community</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">Build an AI Email Responder with OpenAI & Azure</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">Learn how to automate customer support and repetitive queries using OpenAI and Azure Communication Services in this detailed guide.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Read Article <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
			<!-- Video Card 3 -->
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BenjvaGYIwM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block min-w-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-red-200 hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded border border-red-100 bg-red-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-red-600">Video</span>
					<span class="text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">DeepSeek Tutorial</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 break-words text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-slate-900 transition-colors group-hover:text-indigo-600 sm:text-xl">Run DeepSeek-R1 Offline: Chat Interface + PDF RAG</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2">In this video, I’ll show you exactly how to deploy DeepSeek-R1 locally with a clean, modern chat interface and PDF RAG capabilities.</p>
				<span class="text-indigo-600 text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
					Watch Video <span class="ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
				</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Proof Metrics Strip -->
