						Portfolio artifact
					</span>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-4">
					Beginner-friendly ML course covering core concepts with hands-on Python and scikit-learn.
				</p>
				<ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-2 mb-6 flex-grow list-disc pl-5 marker:text-slate-300">
					<li>Core ML concepts (NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib)</li>
